data.description:
Large Corner lot on a Cul De Sac with RV gate. Open floor plan, vaulted ceilings, covered patio, irrigation system front and back, house is conveniently located a block away from South Lake and close to North Lake. 2 members only club houses, with gyms, libraries, restaurant and bars in both club houses as well as yacht club, water park, basket, tennis and volley ball courts. Plenty of biking and hiking trails plus a Golf Course in the community! Stainless steel fridge, range, microwave and dishwasher (BRAND NEW)
OWNER IS A LICENSED ARIZONA REALTOR
